{
  "stem": "10862.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that night my sister came back from working in the field all day, and she was very, very angry because she had risked her life in order to bring in the potatoes so we could eat, and I gave it away.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember my sister gave me such a beating.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I reminded this my sister many, many years ago-- as a matter of fact, because she does not remember doing that to me at all-- and I said, don't you remember?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You hit me so hard, and I cried because I gave away the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, but why did you do it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, well, they told me they were hungry, and they wanted the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that story has always stuck in my mind too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember it, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's things like this that you, you can't forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was Demblin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But life was pretty much routine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you'd get up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called you for an appel to count your numbers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called you by your number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We all had numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On our necks, wore metal pieces of numbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you were lucky that day if they did not select another group to take out someplace else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The women went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The men went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You get the piece of bread and the little, dirty boil of soup, and that was life for two years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was nothing else to do, plus the dirt and everything else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1944, like I said, when the-- when the Germ-- the Russians were coming closer and the Germans were realizing that the war is getting closer to an end, they transferred us to Czestochowa, also in Poland.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
